{"tid":1663162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"敦促蘋果恢復香港地圖APP , 美國參眾議員：庫克別成北京共謀","createTime":"2019-10-19T08:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T09:31:18.000Z","uid":25468,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3681f80c1cf11b61a25bf92b85854276069be4","tid":1663162,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4398238/l/2d9acba4828eccddae97788c4ece9b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4398238%2Fl%2F2d9acba4828eccddae97788c4ece9b8b.jpg&h=a3085e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中事件延燒，港民示威抗議爆發警民激烈衝突，「HKmap.live 即時地圖」遭蘋果 (AAP-US) 下架，引發週五 (18 日) 美國參眾兩院議員痛批，蘋果是應中國政府要求，對香港地圖應用程式進行審查。<br />\n<br />\n「HKmap.live 即時地圖」應用程式是一款能追蹤香港警察及示威活動位置，蘋果以危害執法人員和香港居民，威脅到了公共安全為由下架。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國參眾兩院議員週五致信蘋果 CEO 庫克信中寫道：「蘋果上週採納中國政府意見，下架香港地圖 APP 的決定令人深感憂慮，敦促蘋果易轍改弦，證明蘋果將價值觀置於市場准入之上，並與在香港為基本權利和尊嚴而戰的民眾站在一起。</strong><br />\n<br />\n內容還提到：「你曾公開表示，希望與中國領導人合作實現變革，而非袖手旁觀對他們進行批判。我們也相信，外交和貿易可以使力量民主化。<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但當一個專制政府拒絕改變，或反倒變本加厲時，所稱的合作就會變成共謀</span></strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n這封信是由參議員 Ted Cruz (共和黨)、Ron Wyden (民主黨)、Tom Cotton (共和黨) 和 Marco Rubio (共和黨)，以及眾議員 Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (民主黨 - 紐約)、Mike Gallagher (共和黨 - 維吉尼亞州) 和 Tom Malinowski (民主黨 - 新澤西州) 代表聯合署名。<br />\n<br />\n東西方長袖善舞的蘋果 CEO 庫克早前解釋，國家和國際爭論將持續，但爭論不能影響事實，遭違法惡意利用的爭議地圖徹底審查，相信能保護蘋果用戶。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果庫克從不諱言，中國市場的重要性，除了下架爭議地圖 APP 之外，港版 iPhone 隱藏中華民國 (R.O.C) 國旗表情符號。<br />\n<br />\n2018 年蘋果 2656 億美元的總營收中，大中華地區營收有 510 億美元。蘋果每年生產 2 億多部 iPhone 供應鏈也主要位於中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4398238?exp=a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4398238%3Fexp%3Da&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=7c33c6c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4398238?exp=a</a>"},{"pid":"3e843dbf17dd7de94a9bb1f2355e9578366e823e","tid":1663162,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7821e70b591320fd37e257cf7e449fffb6eb833f","tid":1663162,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"一定唔會恢復，可以放心"},{"pid":"82c7a1f32a664f63f7ba89230c8a44cfe3698c17","tid":1663162,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"【輸出革命】一齊下載強國文宣圖！<br />\n1020 尖東<span style=\"color: red;\">向強國人<strong>輸出革命</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663011\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663011</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4oszVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4oszVJ.jpg&h=a9ec52d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyoz3kZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftyoz3kZ.png&h=39dec6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請入來下載更多文宣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663011\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663011</a>"},{"pid":"7053a3e0f4173dc90f7e5e21b8771cbafe113fc5","tid":1663162,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"自從無左教主，apple已經無曬個人自主氣質"},{"pid":"071187819901e756e3b4cf8208602a4f366d1a54","tid":1663162,"uid":149487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"其實個14億人不嬲講就罷買 但一出都係即刻買架啦 仲衝嚟香港買<br />\n洗鬼怕無生意做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadf768506f79437e2d68b264b1a49eaed3f6d33","tid":1663162,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzMBC